Type casting- converting value of one data type to another

2 Types: widening/implicit/automatic
         narrowing/explicit/manual

Conditional Statements:
1. if statement
2. Switch statement

if statement:

Syntax:
    if(condition) {
            code A;

       }

       ----------------------
       if(condition) {
            code A;
       }else {
            code B;
       }

       -----------------------
       Nested if

       WHAT: if inside another if
       WHY: when we have 1 condition depend on another
       HOW:

       if(condition) { -> outer if


            if(condtion) { -> nested if
       }

       }